    <div class="story-grid">
      <div class="story-content">
        <p class="section-label">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Built on Trust</h2>
        <p class="story-text">Summit Builders was founded in 2001 by Mike Sullivan, a third-generation carpenter who grew up framing houses alongside his father and grandfather in the western suburbs of Chicago.</p>
        <p class="story-text">What started as a two-person crew working out of a garage in Downers Grove has grown into a full-service general contracting firm with a team of 30 skilled tradespeople and project managers. But the philosophy hasn't changed: show up on time, communicate clearly, build it right the first time, and stand behind your work.</p>
        <p class="story-text">Over 25 years, we've completed more than 500 projects — from kitchen remodels to ground-up custom homes to full commercial buildouts. Every one of them started with a conversation and a handshake.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621905252507-b35492cc74b4?w=600&q=80" alt="Construction team reviewing blueprints on site">
